description:
Though she has the same name and an almost identical appearance to http://anidb.net/character/94518 [Sajou Ayaka] from Fate/Prototype, they are actually different people.
[spoiler="Role in Fate/strange Fake"]She is the "True" Master of Saber in the "True and False Holy Grail Wars" of Fate/strange Fake.[/spoiler]
Source: TYPE-MOON wiki
name: Ayaka Sajou
